  <LocalizedText>
    <Text id="LOC_CREATE_PANTHEON_NAME">
      <en_US>[COLOR_FLOAT_SCIENCE]Create Your Pantheon Dev[ENDCOLOR]</en_US>
      <zh_Hans_CN>[COLOR_FLOAT_SCIENCE]创造万神殿 Dev[ENDCOLOR]</zh_Hans_CN>
    </Text>

    <Text id="LOC_CREATE_PANTHEON_AUTHOR">
      <en_US>nea_bahaja,ShizukaMogami,XiMoLan,Phantagonist,PPK; Civ6Mods Dev fixes</en_US>
      <zh_Hans_CN>nea_bahaja,千古歌,夕墨岚,Phantagonist,皮皮凯；Civ6Mods Dev 修复</zh_Hans_CN>
    </Text>

    <Text id="LOC_CREATE_PANTHEON_DESCRIPTION">
      <en_US>Dev fork of Create Your Pantheon. Combos only; AI terrain weights; effects via Gameplay AttachModifier (BeliefModifiers path was a no-op for devotion thresholds). Miracles event+cache. Do NOT enable with the Workshop original.</en_US>
      <zh_Hans_CN>工坊「创造万神殿」本地 Dev：仅组合；AI 地形加权；效果由 Gameplay AttachModifier 挂载（BeliefModifiers 对神力阈值无效）。奇迹事件+缓存。请勿与工坊原版同时启用。</zh_Hans_CN>
    </Text>

    <Text id="LOC_CREATE_PANTHEON_TEASER">
      <en_US>Choose the domain and power to create your unique pantheon. (Dev)</en_US>
      <zh_Hans_CN>选择神格和权柄，创造属于你的万神殿（Dev）</zh_Hans_CN>
    </Text>
  </LocalizedText>
</Mod>
